author: Cathal Kelly
title: Kelly: Jays safe at home in Game 3 as demons exorcized
text: Baseball Ryan Goins got things started offensively for the Blue Jays on Oct. 19 in the American League Championship Series, and maintained his solid defensive play throughout Game 3 to help the team to a victory over Kansas City.
